<br>
In my 40s, I could easily group with people in DL with little wait time on LFG, however as soon as I hit 50, I travelled all over the world, KC, Velks, ME, DSP, hole but did not find many groups successfully and usually spends an hour on lfg before I can start playing.<br>
<br>
One thing I find though is that other players likes to form little groups only, and even when not full group, they will not attempt to form a full group for safety.<br>
<br>
Is my character just getting to a stage that grouping is difficult cause of the psychology of other high level players or is it just cause I am a mage ? if so maybe I should just quit my mage and start a necro cause they seem to be able to solo at all levels and still able to find groups too.<br>
<br>
Or am I simply looking at the wrong places for groups ?<br>
<br>
Any help is appreciated, thanks in advance.<br>
<br>
p.s I play on Tholuxe Paell server<br>
<br>
Vortor Swiftlight<br>
52 Magician <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ubrashnir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Brashnir</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#333333>(3/23/02 11:16:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=163.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home1.gte.net/res0n86l/halo-nos_av.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Difficulty with grouping in 50+ or just cause I am a mag</span><hr size=1> You should have no trouble soloing wyverns in Cobalt Scar at 52.  Rockhoppers in Dawnshroud Peaks should also be easy game.  <br>
<br>
As for grouping, I had a great deal of trouble in my early 50s as well.  The only way I ever got into groups was if my friends who played more &quot;desired&quot; classes invited me, or guild groups.  As I got higher up in my 50s, I got to know more people, and was able to get groups based on my reputation as a good player.  Try to get groups first.  If you can't, fall back on Cobalt scar or DSP.  The mobs are easy and will make your exp bar move up until 55 or 6.  At 56+ I imagine you could solo just fine on golems and skellies in the Grey.  <br>
