<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>Build</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> groups.  For some strategies on building non-standard groups, see: <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showMessage?topicID=3824.topic">The UnHoly Trinity</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.<br>
<br>
Grouping is primarily a social problem, and has less to do with class than is generally supposed.  Master good solo spots with an excess of spawns, and then invite casters to join you.  Works pretty well, and there are more under-utilized spawns than most think.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Razamatazz Pizzazz</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
