 I am a mag</span><hr size=1> Frankly its been a while since I exp grouped to level =)  However I seemed to get the most XP when I tried to stick to a certain crowded zrea like Sebilis and people got to know me.  I also had a group of myself and three others Samila, Lisandre, and Banbanen that I consistantly went to HS with to XP every night.  We all hit 60 there and it was a great time in my EQ XP days.<br>
